FBIS4-14500 "drsov063_f_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-063 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 National Affairs IAEA Experts Concerned About Safety at Chernobyl IAEA Experts Concerned About Safety at Chernobyl LD0104082994 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 0700 GMT 1 Apr 94 LD0104082994 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Ukrainian BFN [Text] Experts from the International Atomic Energy Agency [IAEA] have expressed grave concern about the state of the Chernobyl atomic electric station. Based on an inspection in mid-March, they concluded that the international safety standard could not be guaranteed.
